fulltitle: 'Why Americans Don't Trust Their Media' w/ Robert Parry (2010)
title: 'Why Americans Don't Trust Their Media' w/ Robert Parry (2010)
_filename: _'Why Americans Don't Trust Their Media' w_ Robert Parry (2010).mp4
description:
Created by Justice Action Media https://vimeo.com/justiceactionmedia and Maverick Media: https://maverickmedia.wordpress.com/ ORIGINAL: https://vimeo.com/14326258

Part 1 of interview with Robert Parry, investigative reporter, author and editor of http://www.Consortiumnews.com, by Cindy Piester of Pulse TV. Discuss how media has changed from the 1970s to today, including Vietnam, Iran-Contra, Iraq and Afghanistan. Filmed in Venice, CA on Feb. 18, 2010.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
